'''Mistwater''' was an ultrapure water collected from the condensation of clouds over the planet [[Barnaba]] in the [[Tapani sector/Legends|Tapani sector]]. During the [[Imperial Era/Legends|Imperial Era]] it demanded a high price throughout the Tapani sector and was available to the diners at the [[Vor-cal Feast]] prior to the [[Battle of Endor/Legends|Battle of Endor]].

